Very good. One site I found that was bugged in developer tools is medium.com. Here's how it was when I installed:

{
"url": "medium.com",
"noinvert": ".canvas-renderer"
},

Now remove the '.' before 'canvas'.

{
"url": "medium.com",
"noinvert": "canvas-renderer"
},

And it works. Thanks dev for your work :)

Just brilliant! (y)
I especially love the functionality of white listing some sites :)

@Dev: do you take donations. Coz it deserves some :)
